Closed system.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
The similar scheme we use to simulate the gel in closed system.
 The procedure represents a chain of subsequent MD and MC simulation, but
 now we run the molecular dynamics in two simulation boxes simultaneously.
 The first box of the volume 
\begin_inset Formula $\Vgel$
\end_inset

 contains the gel with ions, and the second box, 
\begin_inset Formula $\Vout$
\end_inset

— contains only ions.
 These two boxes are represented in Figure
\begin_inset space ~
\end_inset


