reference "fig:diamond"

\end_inset

.
 The total volume of both boxes is kept constant, 
\begin_inset Formula $V=V_{\mathrm{gel}}+V_{\mathrm{out}}$
\end_inset

, so the compression of the gel implies the decrease 
\begin_inset Formula $\Vgel$
\end_inset

 and increase 
